docs {
  ###############
  Docs:

  filter type : number
  filter ops : greater_than/less_than/equals/not_equals/greater_than_or_equal/less_than_or_equal/between/not_in_between
  filter value : a single number, for operations like between and not_in_between, it will be a list of two numbers

  filter type : text
  filter ops : contains, not_contains, equals, not_equals, starts_with, ends_with, in, not_in

  filter type : boolean
  filter ops : this parameter is not used in boolean fields
  filter value : true/false

  ####################

